```

Key content absorbed: dependency-order fix sequencing (dataclass → parser → builder → tests),
run tests after each category not at end, grep for all consumers before removing any field,
hidden consumer patterns (`Match.aes_url`, `FollowOnEdge.target_slot`), deferred ranking-end
bug pattern, TaskCreate-before-coding discipline.

