cherry-pick vs narrow-patch approach, fence arithmetic floor issues.

Verified: 1,667→1,625 files (41 removed, 4-phase); 982 files after 2026-05-04 full-corpus
dedup (677 removed); 967→935 entries in 12-cluster Myrmidon swarm consolidation.

